Global Obesity Treatment Devices Market Insights
Obesity Treatment Devices Market size was valued at USD 4.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.35 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Obesity Treatment Devices Market Overview
The global obesity treatment devices market was valued at approximately $2.8 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach about $6.4 billion by 2032, growing at a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of 9.4% during the forecast period. This growth is primarily driven by the increasing prevalence of obesity worldwide, coupled with advancements in medical technology and rising awareness about obesity-related health risks. The escalating prevalence of obesity, technological advancements in medical devices, and increasing awareness about health risks associated with obesity are key factors contributing to market growth. Additionally, the adoption of minimally invasive procedures for weight loss is further propelling market expansion. Source

